meta.description: An unBEElievable dimension full of bees that becomes REALLY angry if you take their honey!
meta.long_description:
![The banner logo for The Bumblezone with a friendly and hostile bee shown below the mod name.](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/40846040/211122783-e4bde0e7-f721-48aa-8095-54dd8319ed40.png) # **1.20.1 OR NEWER MC RECOMMENDED** ###### [[Click here for the NeoForge/Forge version of this mod!]](https://modrinth.com/mod/the-bumblezone) ###### Bumblezone's code is LGPLv3 License while its assets are ARR. The actual jar itself is ARR as a result but you are free to look at and use Bumblezone's open source code! ## **WHAT IS THE BUMBLEZONE?**     The Bumblezone is a bee dimension filled with many brand new bee-related blocks! There's even quite a few structures to explore and a unique bee armor you can obtain! If you are lucky, you may find a special Throne-Locating Honey Compasses from certain structures that leads you to a Bee Queen! The dimension itself looks like it is the inside of a bee nest and you will find giant walls in rows with canals of water between them. Maybe you'll even find a pollen covered section of the dimension or a canyon full of massive honey-based crystals! Check the Bumblezone advancements tab for how to enter dimension and what to do!     Also, you will find bees are extremely protective of their honey in this dimension. If you mine vanilla's Honey Block, destroy or take honey from Honeycomb Brood Block, or you hit a bee, all bees around you will get many buffs and will become VERY angry at you because you now have the Wrath of the Hive effect! But by feeding bees or the Honeycomb Brood Blocks with the honey foods that you have, you might be able to calm them down. By feeding bees or that brood block, you get Protection of the Hive that makes bees defend you against anyone attacking you! *(You can nerf the bees in the config if you find them too strong or buff them if you want to die!)* **Note:** If you have severe trypophobia and the current Bumblezone textures are too much, you can enable the internal mod Anti-Trypophobia resourcepack by going into the resourcepack screen and move the resourcepack to the top of the right side to activate it. **And yes, you can use this mod in a modpack!**
## **WHAT DOES THIS MOD HAVE?**   Check out the wiki below for all the info! It is kept up to date on latest Bumblezone releases. **[https://github.com/TelepathicGrunt/Bumblezone/wiki](https://github.com/TelepathicGrunt/Bumblezone/wiki)** ![All the Blocks, Items, and Mobs in Bumblezone](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/eA8SXqWL/images/bc1b120f1e7592fcbcbd64f9aa407075436976ec.png)  
**If you find an issue, glitch, or have a suggestion about my mod, let me know! But if you don't have a GitHub account to report in the Issue tab above, just comment what the problem is below and I'll try and get back to you ASAP! :)**   **Discord Link to #telepathicgrunt-mods channel for my mods!** **[https://discord.gg/K8qRev3yKZ](https://discord.gg/K8qRev3yKZ)** **My Ko-fi page if you wish to help donate to support me!** **[https://ko-fi.com/telepathicgrunt](https://ko-fi.com/telepathicgrunt)**
